 the distance from durban to cape town.";i:43;s:59:"My friend’s game reserve in the free state near heilbron;";i:44;s:61:"Slept at the elephant’s footprint guesthouse in colchester;";i:45;s:47:"Colesberg, a small town with a famous big hill;";i:46;s:128:"Here i’m going to lay out a simple but long driving route starting in cape town and following the coast all the way to durban.";i:47;s:47:"Johannesburg to cape town via the garden route.";i:48;s:163:"Our itinerary includes the entire route from cape town to port elizabeth, since there are several very worthwhile places to visit just outside of the garden route.";i:49;s:48:"A third route offers a bit of country and coast.";i:50;s:75:"It takes around 1181 to reach durban to cape town via garden route gateway.";i:51;s:30:"The garden route and route 62.";i:52;s:147:"Get up early for a dawn patrol of the bushveld in a safari vehicle, relax in your luxurious chalet perched on the edge of the wild bush, or plunge.";i:53;s:321:"If you planning your south africa holiday, you simply can’t go wrong with the garden route.officially running along the n2 from cape town to mossel bay and then along the coast to port elizabeth, this tour will give you extra stops along the way to make sure you get the absolute best from your south africa road trip!.";i:54;s:151:"Here is our 7 day itinerary along the southern coast of south africa, one of our most thrilling, most enjoyable weeks during our trip around the world.";i:55;s:133:"Your garden route self drive tour comes to an end today in the famous city of cape town in the western cape province of south africa.";i:56;s:63:"You can’t help but be seduced by the glorious natural beauty.";i:57;s:76:"We could probably write a whole novel about this unique, buzzing metropolis.";i:58;s:77:"Kruger national park pilanesberg cape vidal forever resorts durban cape town.";i:59;s:80:"The tour ends in cape town, situated in the southwestern corner of south africa!";i:60;s:25:"Maps of the garden route.";i:61;s:190:"You could call this route the ‘country to coast’ option, as it travels through the natal midlands and bloemfontein, winding its way down to the scenic coastal beauty of the garden route.";i:62;s:79:"Discover and book 4 day garden route private tour from cape town on tripadvisor";i:63;s:193:"To find the driving direction from durban to cape town via garden route gateway which is 1697 by road, click on show directions after entering start and end locations in the calculator control.";}}